data.description: One Level Living!! Over 1/3 Acre Lot with a fully fenced Backyard. Beautifully RENOVATED home in sought after Riverside! All updates completed within the last 5 years!! Kitchen remodel includes cabinets, stainless steal appliances and granite counters. Bathroom has been beautifully renovated with new everything!! Gas Fireplace. Huge fenced backyard, Fence new 2021. 5 YEAR Young ROOF on all structures-House/detached 548 sqft Garage/workshop/Shed. 5 years-HVAC/ductwork, kitchen, bathroom, windows, storm doors on house/garage/shed, Updated siding/gutters/soffits. Refinished hardwood flooring, Updated Tile Floors in entryway, kitchen and bath. All appliances convey. Detached Garage with WORKSHOP. Separate, Detached Shed. This Property is IMMACULATE!!! Enjoy all Riverside has to offer including Private Beach Access. Near by to CNU, Riverside Hospital, The Shipyard, and I-64.
